snippet.title: ASGARD DUNGEON: Heimdallr and Thor Preview - Beneath the Nexus
snippet.description:
https://playbtn.com/
https://aced.gg/

Early preview of the Asgard dungeon. Some things in this dungeon, like dialogue, aren't done at all.

Video music from HeatleyBros. They are great! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o4tTGLfOG7c
